The '''Crocus''' is a [[Flowers|flower]] found via [[Foraging]] in [[Winter]]. It can be found in [[Pelican Town]], the [[Railroad]], the [[Bus Stop]], [[the Mountain]]s, [[Cindersap Forest]], or the [[Backwoods]]. It can also be grown from [[Winter Seeds|Winter wild seeds]].

==Healing==
The Crocus is edible, but does not increase [[Energy]] or [[Health]].

